        <mxCell id="df-rationale" value="&lt;b&gt;Rationale&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px;color:#555&quot;&gt;1. Access issue flagged -- date moved from Nov 15 to Nov 17&lt;br&gt;2. Working at height identified -- hard hat required&lt;br&gt;3. FTTP installation -- standard fibre toolkit needed&lt;br&gt;4. Historical delays: 20 past delays including wayleave&lt;br&gt;5. High risk of further delays based on delay pattern&lt;/font&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=10;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=6;arcSize=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
